(Cho Eun Byul)

264
00:13:46,982 --> 00:13:48,082
But I did.

265
00:13:48,812 --> 00:13:50,782
I knew I wouldn't get it,

266
00:13:51,252 --> 00:13:53,782
but I still wanted to show...

267
00:13:54,292 --> 00:13:56,322
my feelings for Eun Byul one way or another.

268
00:13:57,122 --> 00:14:01,592
But doing it so upfront seemed impossible,

269
00:14:02,162 --> 00:14:05,332
so I expressed it in a way only I would know.

270
00:14:06,562 --> 00:14:09,232
- Jae Seung.
- I'm getting emotional.

271
00:14:10,532 --> 00:14:13,401
Even we're heartbroken.

272
00:14:13,402 --> 00:14:15,442
It hurts so much.

273
00:14:16,912 --> 00:14:20,682
(Jae Seung's feelings are kept within his phone.)

274
00:14:21,712 --> 00:14:25,152
(Meanwhile, Eun Byul...)

275
00:14:29,722 --> 00:14:31,362
- Eun Byul.
- It's Eun Byul.

276
00:14:31,392 --> 00:14:33,362
Eun Byul could've been quick.

277
00:14:36,062 --> 00:14:38,301
(The text sent before 11:30pm is invalid.)

278
00:14:38,302 --> 00:14:41,232
(You can't win the Late-night Date Pass.)

279
00:14:41,502 --> 00:14:43,672
(She sent it before the submission time?)

280
00:14:45,542 --> 00:14:48,872
When I got the text... This is really embarrassing.

281
00:14:49,412 --> 00:14:52,882
I replied the minute I spotted "1st-come, 1st-served..."

282
00:14:52,982 --> 00:14:54,412
without reading...

283
00:14:54,752 --> 00:14:56,382
the rest of the text.

284
00:14:59,052 --> 00:15:01,452
(They get a notice at 11pm.)

285
00:15:01,834 --> 00:15:05,574
("Shin Jae Hyuk" at 11:02pm)

286
00:15:06,022 --> 00:15:07,631
(She instantly replied.)

287
00:15:07,632 --> 00:15:09,061
- That was too soon!
- Sung Mi.

288
00:15:09,062 --> 00:15:10,762
- That was way too soon.
- Eun Byul...

289
00:15:12,402 --> 00:15:13,962
She replied at 11pm.

290
00:15:14,332 --> 00:15:16,371
She took off first in a 100m race.

291
00:15:16,372 --> 00:15:17,472
You're right.

292
00:15:18,672 --> 00:15:20,872
My ears are turning red.

293
00:15:22,142 --> 00:15:23,342
I was so embarrassed.

294
00:15:25,782 --> 00:15:29,982
(Her vote didn't count because she was too impatient.)

295
00:15:32,322 --> 00:15:35,252
(What's Seo Yoon's result?)

296
00:15:39,262 --> 00:15:40,521
Then, the chance goes to...

297
00:15:40,522 --> 00:15:41,762
(Did Seo Yoon seize the opportunity?)

298
00:15:45,162 --> 00:15:46,761
(Due to a late request,)

299
00:15:46,762 --> 00:15:49,071
(Woo Seo Yoon cannot receive the Late-night Date Pass.)

300
00:15:49,072 --> 00:15:50,102
What?

301
00:15:50,842 --> 00:15:52,472
- Oh, no.
- She was late.

302
00:15:52,841 --> 00:15:54,071
Seo Yoon was also late.

303
00:15:56,342 --> 00:16:01,082
(With Seo Yoon out of the picture,)

304
00:16:01,452 --> 00:16:02,881
(there are only Si Woo,)

305
00:16:02,882 --> 00:16:04,521
(Hee Dong,)

306
00:16:04,522 --> 00:16:06,652
(and Jae Hyuk remaining.)

307
00:16:07,522 --> 00:16:11,962
(Who will get the Date Pass?)

308
00:16:12,395 --> 00:16:13,794
(There are only Si Woo,)

309
00:16:13,795 --> 00:16:15,464
(Hee Dong,)

310
00:16:15,465 --> 00:16:17,505
(and Jae Hyuk remaining.)

311
00:16:18,505 --> 00:16:23,105
(Who will get the Date Pass?)

312
00:16:31,485 --> 00:16:32,855
- He got a text.
- There's a text.

313
00:16:35,225 --> 00:16:37,384
(The Late-night Date Pass is given to Shin Jae Hyuk,)

314
00:16:37,385 --> 00:16:39,725
(who requested it first.)

315
00:16:40,155 --> 00:16:42,464
(It was Jae Hyuk.)

316
00:16:42,465 --> 00:16:43,924
- Jae Hyuk!
- He has...

317
00:16:43,925 --> 00:16:45,464
- fast hands.
- He's got fast hands.

318
00:16:45,465 --> 00:16:46,894
He has athletic hands.

319
00:16:46,895 --> 00:16:49,434
- Is he an attacker?
- Yes, he's a right-wing.

320
00:16:49,435 --> 00:16:50,635
He's a right-wing.

321
00:16:51,305 --> 00:16:52,604
- Yes!
- Goodness.

322
00:16:52,605 --> 00:16:54,544
- It was about time he scored.
- Yes.

323
00:16:54,545 --> 00:16:56,845
- You were frustrated at first.
- I know!

324
00:16:57,275 --> 00:16:58,574
- Now, things are looking up.
- He was dribbling back,

325
00:16:58,575 --> 00:16:59,845
and now he's dribbling forward.

326
00:17:00,045 --> 00:17:02,184
He penetrated enemy territory.

327
00:17:02,185 --> 00:17:03,884
- Exactly.
- He's very pleased.

328
00:17:03,885 --> 00:17:05,415
I got so worked up just now.

329
00:17:06,815 --> 00:17:09,284
(You have the Late-night Date Pass,)

330
00:17:09,285 --> 00:17:11,855
(so you may ask out the person you wrote in the text.)

331
00:17:13,825 --> 00:17:15,694
- Really?
- "Go on a date with me."

332
00:17:15,695 --> 00:17:16,794
- Like that.
- Really?

333
00:17:16,795 --> 00:17:18,564
- Who will he ask out?
- Now, it's a matter...

334
00:17:18,565 --> 00:17:20,035
of whom he'll ask out.

335
00:17:20,165 --> 00:17:22,865
- Will it be Eun Byul or Seo Yoon?
- Eun Byul or Seo Yoon.

336
00:17:38,555 --> 00:17:40,185
- It's Eun Byul.
- It's Eun Byul.

337
00:17:40,755 --> 00:17:41,924
- Is it?
- Eun Byul?

338
00:17:41,925 --> 00:17:43,085
(Will he ask out Eun Byul?)

339
00:17:45,395 --> 00:17:46,525
(Glancing)

340
00:17:52,635 --> 00:17:53,795
- Is it Seo Yoon?
- Is it Seo Yoon?

341
00:17:54,065 --> 00:17:55,334
- What's going on?
- Who is it?

342
00:17:55,335 --> 00:17:56,465
Seo Yoon?

343
00:17:57,935 --> 00:18:00,435
I can't watch this, Jae Hyuk.

344
00:18:01,005 --> 00:18:03,675
- Who is it?
- He must ask her out now.

345
00:18:03,775 --> 00:18:05,275
- But he sat next to Eun Byul.
- Who?

346
00:18:15,785 --> 00:18:18,255
Can you show me how you look in glasses later?

347
00:18:18,495 --> 00:18:20,424
Should I wear them now?

348
00:18:20,425 --> 00:18:21,425
Sure.

349
00:18:23,595 --> 00:18:25,094
(They talked about glasses...)

350
00:18:25,095 --> 00:18:27,265
(during the 2nd-choice date.)

351
00:18:27,635 --> 00:18:30,135
(Do you want to switch glasses with me?)

352
00:18:30,535 --> 00:18:33,175
(They promised to try on each other's glasses.)

353
00:18:34,745 --> 00:18:36,245
- Do you want me to come with you?
- Yes.

354
00:18:37,605 --> 00:18:39,175
- Are you embarrassed?
- Yes.

355
00:18:40,015 --> 00:18:41,785
I don't think I can come here wearing them.

356
00:18:43,115 --> 00:18:44,555
How about I wear them?

357
00:18:48,425 --> 00:18:50,484
They're similar to yours.

358
00:18:50,485 --> 00:18:52,754
(He hands over his glasses.)

359
00:18:52,755 --> 00:18:54,124
This is the pair I wore every morning.

360
00:18:54,125 --> 00:18:56,324
- What?
- Was it at the barbecue?

361
00:18:56,325 --> 00:18:57,665
(She tries on his glasses.)

362
00:18:57,935 --> 00:18:59,135
Which one is better?

363
00:18:59,335 --> 00:19:00,795
You look good in both.

364
00:19:01,905 --> 00:19:03,135
Do I look good in them?

365
00:19:03,965 --> 00:19:05,235
Honestly?

366
00:19:06,335 --> 00:19:10,205
(They both try on Jae Hyuk's glasses.)

367
00:19:10,375 --> 00:19:12,015
Good. I wish I could take a photo of you.

368
00:19:14,275 --> 00:19:16,015
- Here we go again.
- Do we have to pose again?

369
00:19:17,115 --> 00:19:18,885
(Clicking)

370
00:19:24,355 --> 00:19:26,054
- Even if the glasses are pretty...
- Yes, pretty glasses.

371
00:19:26,055 --> 00:19:27,864
No, I mean, even if they're pretty, they don't look good on everyone.

372
00:19:27,865 --> 00:19:28,865
Right.

373
00:19:30,325 --> 00:19:31,434
It suits you.

374
00:19:31,435 --> 00:19:32,835
- You should have it.
- Okay.

375
00:19:33,235 --> 00:19:34,505
- It's mine now.
- Thank you.

376
00:19:34,965 --> 00:19:37,205
(Amazed)

377
00:19:37,805 --> 00:19:40,275
(What a cute couple.)

378
00:19:40,475 --> 00:19:42,574
- So, who did he pick?
- I know, right?

379
00:19:42,575 --> 00:19:44,405
Was that him asking her out?

380
00:19:45,475 --> 00:19:46,644
He hasn't asked her out yet.

381
00:19:46,645 --> 00:19:47,775
- No.
- Not yet.

382
00:19:48,645 --> 00:19:49,914
He's keeping all of us on the edges of our seats.

383
00:19:49,915 --> 00:19:51,385
Why is he hesitating?

384
00:19:51,515 --> 00:19:55,054
I have a feeling that he feels bad about going on a date,

385
00:19:55,055 --> 00:19:57,285
so he's spending time with Eun Byul.

386
00:19:57,655 --> 00:19:59,324
- Then, he'll ask out Seo Yoon...
- Oh, no.

387
00:19:59,325 --> 00:20:00,695
later.

388
00:20:00,855 --> 00:20:04,024
I assume it's his strategy to naturally ask her out...

389
00:20:04,025 --> 00:20:05,694
on a date...

390
00:20:05,695 --> 00:20:07,834
- at the perfect moment.
- Right.

391
00:20:07,835 --> 00:20:10,164
But isn't he hesitating for too long?

392
00:20:10,165 --> 00:20:12,205
(Very curious about what's on Jae Hyuk's mind)

393
00:20:14,135 --> 00:20:15,545
Do I look okay?

394
00:20:16,445 --> 00:20:17,874
You do.

395
00:20:17,875 --> 00:20:19,675
Do you want to take a photo in these?

396
00:20:20,675 --> 00:20:21,714
- In these?
- Yes.

397
00:20:21,715 --> 00:20:22,785
Deal.

398
00:20:26,685 --> 00:20:27,754
(Eun Byul exclaiming)

399
00:20:27,755 --> 00:20:28,885
He's spacing out.

400
00:20:34,925 --> 00:20:36,995
I feel so bad for Jae Seung.

401
00:20:37,625 --> 00:20:39,835
- Oh, my gosh!
- Jae Seung.

402
00:20:40,335 --> 00:20:42,564
(Love is)

403
00:20:42,565 --> 00:20:43,604
Oh, no!

404
00:20:43,605 --> 00:20:46,805
(Though you can't say it)

405
00:20:47,175 --> 00:20:50,174
(Depressed)

406
00:20:50,175 --> 00:20:51,614
Why is he sitting there? Just go to bed.

407
00:20:51,615 --> 00:20:52,875
Jae Seung, just go to bed.

408
00:20:53,115 --> 00:20:54,214
Why...

409
00:20:54,215 --> 00:20:55,715
- We need to hold a book.
- Right.

410
00:20:56,085 --> 00:20:57,684
- In there?
- Yes.

411
00:20:57,685 --> 00:20:58,814
Okay.

412
00:20:58,815 --> 00:21:00,015
(The affectionate couple walks by,)

413
00:21:01,555 --> 00:21:05,725
(and Jae Seung can only pretend not to notice them.)

414
00:21:07,595 --> 00:21:09,964
(To take a photo of themselves in each other's glasses)

415
00:21:09,965 --> 00:21:11,695
I am here.

416
00:21:12,535 --> 00:21:13,564
I look too...

417
00:21:13,565 --> 00:21:15,805
(The two came upstairs to take photos.)

418
00:21:16,565 --> 00:21:19,475
(Jae Hyuk's glasses and Eun Byul's glasses)

419
00:21:20,475 --> 00:21:24,505
(They take a photo together in each other's glasses.)

420
00:21:26,675 --> 00:21:28,085
- It's not bad.
- It's good.

421
00:21:29,045 --> 00:21:31,215
- He got something.
- He got a text message.

422
00:21:32,215 --> 00:21:34,254
(It is now time to head out for your date.)

423
00:21:34,255 --> 00:21:37,155
(Please ask your partner out on a date within 5 minutes.)

424
00:21:49,705 --> 00:21:50,935
I like this photo.

425
00:21:51,605 --> 00:21:53,175
- Yes, it looks good.
- Yes.

426
00:21:54,205 --> 00:21:55,344
Go on a date with me.

427
00:21:55,345 --> 00:21:58,415
(Go on a date with me.)

428
00:21:59,115 --> 00:22:00,174
I knew it!

429
00:22:00,175 --> 00:22:02,114
(Jae Hyuk chose Eun Byul.)

430
00:22:02,115 --> 00:22:04,245
- It was Eun Byul.
- Good.

431
00:22:04,415 --> 00:22:05,555
I told you so.

432
00:22:05,885 --> 00:22:07,715
I told you so.

433
00:22:07,915 --> 00:22:10,455
But Jae Hyuk is...

434
00:22:11,395 --> 00:22:13,154
too good...

435
00:22:13,155 --> 00:22:15,195
- at playing hard to get.
- Right?

436
00:22:15,495 --> 00:22:18,064
Eun Byul and Jae Hyuk are going on a date.

437
00:22:18,065 --> 00:22:19,295
He's so manly.

438
00:22:19,765 --> 00:22:21,365
"Go on a date with me." Good.

439
00:22:21,835 --> 00:22:23,065
Go on a date with me.

440
00:22:23,865 --> 00:22:24,874
What?

441
00:22:24,875 --> 00:22:26,705
(He suddenly asked her out.)

442
00:22:27,605 --> 00:22:29,544
What just happened?

443
00:22:29,545 --> 00:22:31,645
- Get ready and come outside.
- What?

444
00:22:32,875 --> 00:22:34,575
That was so cool.

445
00:22:35,115 --> 00:22:37,145
He's making my heart flutter, even.

446
00:22:38,685 --> 00:22:40,355
(Dazed)

447
00:22:41,215 --> 00:22:42,355
Come here.

448
00:22:43,255 --> 00:22:44,695
Seriously.

449
00:22:45,595 --> 00:22:46,855
I'll show you the text.

450
00:22:47,155 --> 00:22:49,325
"Get ready for the date."

451
00:22:50,395 --> 00:22:52,265
- What?
- I won the Pass.

452
00:22:52,795 --> 00:22:53,995
You sent the request?

453
00:22:54,365 --> 00:22:55,665
Who do you think sent it, then?

454
00:22:57,505 --> 00:22:58,634
- Did you?
- You didn't?

455
00:22:58,635 --> 00:22:59,705
Did you send it?

456
00:23:00,235 --> 00:23:01,874
- Did you not send it?
- I mean...

457
00:23:01,875 --> 00:23:03,605
Can you answer my question first?

458
00:23:05,415 --> 00:23:06,875
I did.

459
00:23:08,715 --> 00:23:09,885
Was it...

460
00:23:11,355 --> 00:23:12,385
Did you...

461
00:23:13,955 --> 00:23:15,025
pick me?

462
00:23:15,425 --> 00:23:16,485
Yes.

463
00:23:18,955 --> 00:23:20,094
I see.

464
00:23:20,095 --> 00:23:21,594
- Is that what you're wearing?
- No.

465
00:23:21,595 --> 00:23:24,124
- I'm getting changed.
- If that's what you want to wear,

466
00:23:24,125 --> 00:23:25,794
- I'll wear something similar.
- No, I...

467
00:23:25,795 --> 00:23:27,235
No, I'll change.

468
00:23:28,705 --> 00:23:31,835
I actually had two on my mind, right?

469
00:23:32,205 --> 00:23:35,545
But Eun Byul is still the first one...

470
00:23:36,675 --> 00:23:38,075
to come to my mind.

471
00:23:40,315 --> 00:23:41,985
During the date,

472
00:23:42,245 --> 00:23:45,255
what Eun Byul said...

473
00:23:45,885 --> 00:23:49,085
hit home.

474
00:23:50,555 --> 00:23:55,365
(I got to try all types of new things with you that day.)

475
00:23:55,725 --> 00:23:58,935
(I had fun, thanks to Jae Hyuk.)

476
00:24:01,905 --> 00:24:03,934
Being able to give someone...

477
00:24:03,935 --> 00:24:05,604
a new experience...

478
00:24:05,605 --> 00:24:09,604
and to make the person happy to have experienced that...

479
00:24:09,605 --> 00:24:11,045
made me feel proud,

480
00:24:11,245 --> 00:24:13,614
and I wanted...

481
00:24:13,615 --> 00:24:17,115
to give her more.

482
00:24:17,515 --> 00:24:20,455
That's why I chose Eun Byul.

483
00:24:21,425 --> 00:24:22,425
I sent it.

484
00:24:23,055 --> 00:24:24,055
Well done.

485
00:24:24,055 --> 00:24:25,055
(He had chosen Eun Byul as his date.)

486
00:24:25,355 --> 00:24:27,655
(Putting on lip balm)

487
00:24:28,025 --> 00:24:31,295
(Eun Byul is getting ready for a Late-night Date.)

488
00:24:31,495 --> 00:24:36,035
I realized that Jae Hyuk had requested it and won,

489
00:24:36,735 --> 00:24:38,605
so I was touched.

490
00:24:38,635 --> 00:24:40,705
That was my impression.

491
00:24:41,545 --> 00:24:44,045
(Smiling)

492
00:24:44,475 --> 00:24:47,475
It does make one's heart flutter.

493
00:24:49,615 --> 00:24:54,155
(Jae Hyuk also checks how he looks before the date.)

494
00:24:56,055 --> 00:24:57,654
(Spraying)

495
00:24:57,655 --> 00:25:00,624
(Spraying)

496
00:25:00,625 --> 00:25:01,625
(He generously applies perfume.)

497
00:25:01,625 --> 00:25:02,625
Perfume!

498
00:25:03,125 --> 00:25:05,295
- Oh, my goodness.
- Stop spraying it!

499
00:25:05,865 --> 00:25:06,894
- Hey!
- Hey!

500
00:25:06,895 --> 00:25:08,835
- That's too much!
- Jae Hyuk!

501
00:25:08,935 --> 00:25:10,565
You might as well shower in it.

502
00:25:11,405 --> 00:25:12,834
It's supposed to be subtle.

503
00:25:12,835 --> 00:25:13,835
(Laughing)

504
00:25:16,575 --> 00:25:17,745
It must have snowed.

505
00:25:18,045 --> 00:25:19,275
- What?
- It snowed.

506
00:25:20,845 --> 00:25:23,144
I'm serious. It snowed.

507
00:25:23,145 --> 00:25:24,315
- Oh, it did.
- Yes.

508
00:25:24,545 --> 00:25:25,554
That's what I said.

509
00:25:25,555 --> 00:25:26,555
(It snowed as if it were celebrating their date.)

510
00:25:27,585 --> 00:25:30,054
(On the Unlimited Late-night Date with excitement)

511
00:25:30,055 --> 00:25:31,184
Going on dates during the day...

512
00:25:31,185 --> 00:25:32,694
- and at night are very different.
- It's different.

513
00:25:32,695 --> 00:25:34,154
It makes you sentimental.

514
00:25:34,155 --> 00:25:36,025
And the level of focus.

515
00:25:37,565 --> 00:25:39,835
Sung Mi is...

516
00:25:40,665 --> 00:25:42,934
Are they going somewhere secluded?

517
00:25:42,935 --> 00:25:44,034
Yes, now.

518
00:25:44,035 --> 00:25:45,535
All night.

519
00:25:45,675 --> 00:25:46,905
Oh, dear.

520
00:25:47,305 --> 00:25:49,644
Is there anything you want to tell Jae Hyuk right now?

521
00:25:49,645 --> 00:25:51,744
- Tell him?
- To your boy.

522
00:25:51,745 --> 00:25:53,614
- No.
- Nothing?

523
00:25:53,615 --> 00:25:55,545
- Just do it.
- Just do it?

524
00:25:55,815 --> 00:25:57,144
"Just follow your heart."

525
00:25:57,145 --> 00:25:58,384
They'll fall hard for each other.

