792
00:41:21,705 --> 00:41:22,845
I think so too.

793
00:41:24,775 --> 00:41:26,344
Exactly, you jerk.

794
00:41:26,345 --> 00:41:27,445
Why am I a jerk?

795
00:41:27,875 --> 00:41:31,645
You knew it all along, but you kept quiet all this while.

796
00:41:36,425 --> 00:41:40,655
I didn't know Si Woo would think to that extent.

797
00:41:41,695 --> 00:41:43,594
Still, I think...

798
00:41:43,595 --> 00:41:46,495
