799
00:41:48,865 --> 00:41:50,205
I was relieved.

800
00:41:58,645 --> 00:42:01,975
(After finishing the happy conversation,)

801
00:42:02,645 --> 00:42:07,555
(Hee Dong and Si Woo head to the Photo Room.)

802
00:42:08,255 --> 00:42:10,285
Did you send the text? The 11:30pm one?

803
00:42:10,885 --> 00:42:11,955
That?

804
00:42:13,825 --> 00:42:14,825
- No.
- You didn't?

805
00:42:15,595 --> 00:42:17,025
- Did you?
- No, I didn't either.

806
00:42:18,195 --> 00:42:19,895
- Why didn't you?
- Why didn't I?

807
00:42:20,635 --> 00:42:21,895
Because I thought you wouldn't.

808
00:42:24,005 --> 00:42:25,035
Really?

809
00:42:26,475 --> 00:42:28,405
