I didn't even think about that.

824
00:43:06,715 --> 00:43:08,845
That's not it.

825
00:43:09,545 --> 00:43:11,084
I thought they were two different things.

826
00:43:11,085 --> 00:43:13,854
That's not it. I thought they were two different things.

827
00:43:13,855 --> 00:43:14,914
What are two different things?

828
00:43:14,915 --> 00:43:17,485
