829
00:43:18,785 --> 00:43:21,395
I'm glad they cleared the misunderstanding.

830
00:43:23,295 --> 00:43:24,565
Let's make up.

831
00:43:28,135 --> 00:43:29,635
Because of the promise,

832
00:43:30,335 --> 00:43:32,305
