843
00:44:04,165 --> 00:44:06,405
Why didn't you grow taller?

844
00:44:06,775 --> 00:44:07,905
Come here.

845
00:44:08,105 --> 00:44:10,205
No, come here.

846
00:44:10,975 --> 00:44:12,205
