855
00:44:34,635 --> 00:44:36,065
Tae Woong, treat us.

856
00:44:37,805 --> 00:44:38,904
- Sure.
- A few days ago,

857
00:44:38,905 --> 00:44:40,005
for the first time in a while,

858
00:44:40,205 --> 00:44:42,605
