860
00:44:45,575 --> 00:44:47,344
- Good job.
- The four-frame photo.

861
00:44:47,345 --> 00:44:48,544
- Okay.
- Good to know.

862
00:44:48,545 --> 00:44:50,445
- We heard you.
- Goodness.

863
00:44:50,645 --> 00:44:51,944
