- Yes.

916
00:47:18,925 --> 00:47:20,235
I wonder what the others are doing.

917
00:47:21,065 --> 00:47:24,004
- What will happen tomorrow?
- What are they doing?

918
00:47:24,005 --> 00:47:25,335
What will happen tomorrow?

919
00:47:25,405 --> 00:47:27,105
