- and Hee Dong.

925
00:47:38,115 --> 00:47:39,215
- Really?
- Yes.

926
00:47:40,855 --> 00:47:42,715
You won't end up not choosing me after all this, will you?

927
00:47:45,885 --> 00:47:46,925
Me?

928
