938
00:48:20,925 --> 00:48:22,595
I had butterflies in my stomach, of course.

939
00:48:23,695 --> 00:48:26,665
It's not a chance anybody can have.

940
00:48:27,235 --> 00:48:29,765
We got to spend more time on our own.

941
00:48:30,265 --> 00:48:32,305
Compared to the first date,

942
00:48:33,075 --> 00:48:34,805
