943
00:48:35,805 --> 00:48:38,275
act more comfortably around me.

944
00:48:40,475 --> 00:48:42,075
They don't feel uncomfortable.

945
00:48:42,985 --> 00:48:44,285
Those were the days.

946
00:48:44,885 --> 00:48:47,184
