950
00:48:54,295 --> 00:48:56,094
The groom's father.

951
00:48:56,095 --> 00:48:57,264
The bride's mother.

952
00:48:57,265 --> 00:48:58,824
- Bow at each other.
- Bow at each other.

953
00:48:58,825 --> 00:49:00,435
Bow at each other.

954
00:49:01,335 --> 00:49:03,964
