995
00:50:54,675 --> 00:50:57,645
But that's not the case now,

996
00:50:59,185 --> 00:51:00,485
so I want to talk with him.

997
00:51:00,515 --> 00:51:04,655
Now, I plan to approach him very proactively.

998
00:51:06,555 --> 00:51:07,654
(Seo Yoon decides to go straight for him.)

999
00:51:07,655 --> 00:51:08,894
Things are getting interesting.

1000
00:51:08,895 --> 00:51:11,465
She's getting competitive.

1001
00:51:11,625 --> 00:51:12,825
She's cool.

1002
00:51:12,965 --> 00:51:14,365
She has a chance.

1003
00:51:14,695 --> 00:51:17,065
They're past the halfway mark.

1004
00:51:17,205 --> 00:51:19,305
- She must've felt a lot.
- Yes.

1005
00:51:19,435 --> 00:51:20,474
This is halfway through the fourth quarter,

1006
00:51:20,475 --> 00:51:21,505
- so...
- Is that so?

1007
00:51:21,605 --> 00:51:24,144
if the opponent does pretty well,

1008
00:51:24,145 --> 00:51:25,374
