- The last day?

1049
00:53:16,485 --> 00:53:18,085
They'll make the Final Selection on the next day.

1050
00:53:18,685 --> 00:53:20,155
- I see.
- It's Jae Seung's final chance.

1051
00:53:20,225 --> 00:53:21,995
Write the men's names in the blue section,

1052
00:53:22,395 --> 00:53:23,795
and write the women's names in the red section.

1053
00:53:24,995 --> 00:53:27,964
Next to the name of the person you want to go on a date with,

1054
00:53:27,965 --> 00:53:30,264
write your name yourself.

1055
00:53:30,265 --> 00:53:32,064
(The final 1-on-1 Date: Men's names in the blue section,)

1056
00:53:32,065 --> 00:53:33,174
(women's names in the red section, and you can go on a date...)

1057
00:53:33,175 --> 00:53:34,275
(with the person whose name is written next to yours.)

1058
00:53:34,405 --> 00:53:36,134
It's first-come first-served basis in a way.

1059
00:53:36,135 --> 00:53:37,404
Who writes their name first...

1060
00:53:37,405 --> 00:53:39,075
- is important too.
- That's right.

1061
00:53:39,275 --> 00:53:40,614
And who writes their name...

1062
00:53:40,615 --> 00:53:42,715
- next to yours is important too.
- That's right.

1063
00:53:43,515 --> 00:53:45,685
(An important board has arrived.)

1064
00:53:45,815 --> 00:53:47,285
- It looks pretty.
- Yes.

1065
00:53:47,955 --> 00:53:49,114
It's so pretty.

1066
00:53:49,115 --> 00:53:50,685
(Si Woo and Eun Byul didn't hear the bell.)

1067
00:53:52,325 --> 00:53:54,394
(Jae Hyuk is still sound asleep.)

1068
00:53:54,395 --> 00:53:58,665
(So is Hee Dong.)

1069
00:54:00,435 --> 00:54:02,495
(Everyone is hesitant.)

1070
00:54:02,695 --> 00:54:04,065
- I'll write my name.
- Okay.

1071
00:54:06,575 --> 00:54:08,674
(Hoo writes his name first.)

1072
00:54:08,675 --> 00:54:10,005
Hoo always does things first.

1073
00:54:13,645 --> 00:54:16,414
(Yoon Hoo)

1074
00:54:16,415 --> 00:54:17,834
Is it open? Can I write my name on it?

1075
00:54:20,915 --> 00:54:23,924
It'd be strange for Yu Bin not to write her name next to his.

1076
00:54:23,925 --> 00:54:26,925
She might as well have said, "Write my name next to yours."

1077
00:54:27,095 --> 00:54:28,224
- She has to write it.
- As for Yu Bin...

1078
00:54:28,225 --> 00:54:29,494
- It has to be Hoo.
- Of course.

1079
00:54:29,495 --> 00:54:30,895
- It has to be Hoo.
- That's right.

1080
00:54:35,395 --> 00:54:40,735
(Yu Bin writes down her name.)

1081
00:54:44,546 --> 00:54:46,144
(What?)

1082
00:54:46,145 --> 00:54:48,014
- What?
- I think it's the space below it.

1083
00:54:48,015 --> 00:54:49,015
What?

1084
00:54:49,275 --> 00:54:53,685
(Why is Yu Bin looking down?)

1085
00:54:56,485 --> 00:54:59,255
(Yu Bin wrote her name next to Hoo's.)

1086
00:54:59,625 --> 00:55:01,994
- Gosh, that startled me.
- Seriously.

1087
00:55:01,995 --> 00:55:02,995
That startled me!

1088
00:55:02,996 --> 00:55:05,712
Why did she write her name like this?

1089
00:55:06,735 --> 00:55:08,434
Had she picked something different,

1090
00:55:08,435 --> 00:55:10,105
- it would've been strange.
- I know.

1091
00:55:11,065 --> 00:55:15,005
(They get their second date after the karaoke date.)

1092
00:55:18,145 --> 00:55:21,315
(Jae Seung writes his name next.)

1093
00:55:23,215 --> 00:55:25,284
(Jae Seung)

1094
00:55:25,285 --> 00:55:29,115
I thought that writing my name first would put me more at ease.

1095
00:55:30,525 --> 00:55:33,355
(Whose name do you want to see next to yours?)

1096
00:55:33,755 --> 00:55:35,494
It's a day before the Final Selection,

1097
00:55:35,495 --> 00:55:37,810
so I want to have a date with Eun Byul...

1098
00:55:38,065 --> 00:55:39,394
one last time.

1099
00:55:41,335 --> 00:55:45,105
(Jae Seung wants Eun Byul to write her name next to his.)

1100
00:55:46,935 --> 00:55:49,204
Eun Byul.

1101
00:55:49,205 --> 00:55:50,404
(Whose name will come next to Jae Seung's?)

1102
00:55:50,405 --> 00:55:52,105
I hope things go well for him.

1103
00:55:53,045 --> 00:55:56,785
(It's Seo Yoon's turn to write her name.)

1104
00:55:58,245 --> 00:56:00,655
(She writes her name without hesitation.)

1105
00:56:07,955 --> 00:56:10,324
(Woo Seo Yoon)

1106
00:56:10,325 --> 00:56:14,935
Hoping to get a date with Jae Hyuk,

1107
00:56:15,365 --> 00:56:19,565
I wrote my name on an empty section.

1108
00:56:21,905 --> 00:56:22,905
(Seo Yoon plucks up her courage and puts her name on an empty section.)

1109
00:56:22,906 --> 00:56:25,204
- I see.
- She gave some leeway.

1110
00:56:25,205 --> 00:56:26,845
- It'll be Jae Hyuk or Hee Dong.
- That's right.

1111
00:56:27,245 --> 00:56:28,615
Her date will be Jae Hyuk or Hee Dong.

1112
00:56:28,775 --> 00:56:30,714
- She decided to let them choose.
- Yes.

1113
00:56:30,715 --> 00:56:31,715
(Will Seo Yoon's wish come true?)

1114
00:56:32,845 --> 00:56:35,914
(The next person to spot the board is...)

1115
00:56:35,915 --> 00:56:38,885
(Hee Dong.)

1116
00:56:43,125 --> 00:56:44,864
(1-on-1 Date)

1117
00:56:44,865 --> 00:56:50,165
(Two sections remain.)

1118
00:56:59,645 --> 00:57:04,245
(Where did Hee Dong put his name?)

1119
00:57:05,085 --> 00:57:08,715
(Hee Dong chose an empty section.)

1120
00:57:09,715 --> 00:57:13,285
It looked like we could choose our own dates.

1121
00:57:13,755 --> 00:57:16,324
Si Woo's name wasn't on the board,

1122
00:57:16,325 --> 00:57:18,295
so I put my name on an empty section.

1123
00:57:19,095 --> 00:57:20,965
I want to go on a date with Si Woo.

1124
00:57:23,435 --> 00:57:26,034
- That's right.
- Hee Dong is leaning toward Si Woo.

1125
00:57:26,035 --> 00:57:28,535
- He is smart.
- He is hoping to get Si Woo.

1126
00:57:29,575 --> 00:57:30,845
Is Si Woo...

1127
00:57:31,645 --> 00:57:32,675
still asleep?

1128
00:57:34,315 --> 00:57:35,974
(While Hee Dong worries about Si Woo)

1129
00:57:35,975 --> 00:57:37,645
- Yesterday.
- Yesterday?

1130
00:57:38,215 --> 00:57:40,044
- What happened yesterday?
- I'm so curious.

1131
00:57:40,045 --> 00:57:42,085
- Hello.
- Jealousy kept me up last night.

1132
00:57:42,585 --> 00:57:43,655
Jae Hyuk doesn't know about the board yet.

1133
00:57:44,955 --> 00:57:47,795
Did something happen in the morning?

1134
00:57:47,955 --> 00:57:49,294
What? No.

1135
00:57:49,295 --> 00:57:52,864
Si Woo and Eun Byul haven't come out yet.

1136
00:57:52,865 --> 00:57:54,535
The four of us could eat together.

1137
00:57:55,065 --> 00:57:56,394
Where did you go last night?

1138
00:57:56,395 --> 00:57:57,405
Can't you tell us?

1139
00:57:58,435 --> 00:57:59,435
Okay.

1140
00:58:00,505 --> 00:58:02,905
We just went somewhere.

1141
00:58:03,275 --> 00:58:06,044
You didn't come back until I fell asleep.

1142
00:58:06,045 --> 00:58:08,645
I couldn't believe how late you came back.

1143
00:58:13,485 --> 00:58:16,255
I fell asleep around 4:30am.

1144
00:58:20,195 --> 00:58:22,194
- She sat next to him.
- She sat down.

1145
00:58:22,195 --> 00:58:24,665
We came back around 5:30am or 6am.

1146
00:58:24,825 --> 00:58:26,295
Did you look outside the door?

1147
00:58:27,965 --> 00:58:29,164
Hurry up and check.

1148
00:58:29,165 --> 00:58:30,265
- Is something there?
- Yes.

1149
00:58:30,905 --> 00:58:32,135
Where? Outside? Inside?

1150
00:58:32,335 --> 00:58:34,005
You'll see it when you go outside.

1151
00:58:34,335 --> 00:58:35,375
He didn't see it.

1152
00:58:47,455 --> 00:58:48,515
What is it?

1153
00:58:51,285 --> 00:58:54,995
(He checks the board belatedly.)

1154
00:58:56,865 --> 00:58:59,194
- Jae Hyuk doesn't have a choice.
- No, he doesn't.

1155
00:58:59,195 --> 00:59:01,434
- There is only one empty section.
- That's right.

1156
00:59:01,435 --> 00:59:03,095
- He has to put his name there.
- Exactly.

1157
00:59:09,235 --> 00:59:12,475
All other men's names were on the board.

1158
00:59:12,705 --> 00:59:16,315
The only section that was empty had a woman's name next to it.

1159
00:59:16,475 --> 00:59:18,885
It was Seo Yoon's name.

1160
00:59:30,195 --> 00:59:32,095
The day before,

1161
00:59:32,525 --> 00:59:35,258
I thought my mind was set.

1162
00:59:35,535 --> 00:59:39,505
But I ended up going on another date with Seo Yoon.

1163
00:59:40,165 --> 00:59:42,575
It filled my head with thought.

1164
00:59:46,105 --> 00:59:47,545
I had a lot on my mind,

1165
00:59:48,075 --> 00:59:49,844
but I knew that having these thoughts...

1166
00:59:49,845 --> 00:59:51,715
during the date...

1167
00:59:51,945 --> 00:59:53,785
would be rude to the other person.

1168
00:59:54,085 --> 00:59:57,324
I had a nice date...

1169
00:59:57,325 --> 00:59:59,825
with Seo Yoon last time,

1170
01:00:00,161 --> 01:00:03,808
so I was excited about how the day would go.

1171
01:00:05,925 --> 01:00:09,564
Jae Hyuk wants to talk to Seo Yoon.

1172
01:00:09,565 --> 01:00:10,834
- That's right. Of course.
- Yes.

1173
01:00:10,835 --> 01:00:12,705
- He is still unsure.
- I don't know.

1174
01:00:13,105 --> 01:00:15,535
He is unsure even after spending a night with her.

1175
01:00:15,705 --> 01:00:17,374
He couldn't help but put his name there,

1176
01:00:17,375 --> 01:00:19,975
but this could be a chance for both of them.

1177
01:00:20,815 --> 01:00:25,245
(Yoon Hoo and Choi Yu Bin, Shin Jae Hyuk and Woo Seo Yoon)

1178
01:00:26,415 --> 01:00:27,914
(Si Woo comes to the kitchen.)

1179
01:00:27,915 --> 01:00:29,315
- Hello.
- Hello.

1180
01:00:29,755 --> 01:00:31,485
Why don't you go outside?

1181
01:00:32,355 --> 01:00:33,355
Go outside? Why?

1182
01:00:33,356 --> 01:00:35,124
- Go outside.
- Do you want me to go outside?

1183
01:00:35,125 --> 01:00:36,155
Yes.

1184
01:00:36,255 --> 01:00:37,924
- Do you want me to go outside?
- Yes, go outside.

1185
01:00:37,925 --> 01:00:39,165
You'll find something.

1186
01:00:44,905 --> 01:00:46,635
(What?)

1187
01:00:49,875 --> 01:00:50,875
No way.

1188
01:00:53,105 --> 01:00:57,445
(Two sections next to Jae Seung and Hee Dong's names are empty.)

1189
01:00:58,445 --> 01:00:59,545
Hold on.

1190
01:01:00,755 --> 01:01:01,915
When I went outside,

1191
01:01:02,215 --> 01:01:04,425
I saw that the section next to Hee Dong's name was empty.

1192
01:01:04,885 --> 01:01:06,995
(Looking around)

1193
01:01:07,695 --> 01:01:13,464
(You Hee Dong)

1194
01:01:13,465 --> 01:01:17,435
So I put my name next to his.

1195
01:01:27,215 --> 01:01:30,585
(Feeling shy, she runs away right after writing her name.)

1196
01:01:31,015 --> 01:01:32,044
Is she embarrassed?

1197
01:01:32,045 --> 01:01:33,345
Her steps are light.

1198
01:01:33,685 --> 01:01:35,185
- She is in a good mood.
- Yes.

1199
01:01:35,315 --> 01:01:38,085
I felt like I was getting rewarded...

1200
01:01:38,255 --> 01:01:40,325
for the goals I had.

1201
01:01:40,555 --> 01:01:42,354
I wondered if I had struggled so much...

1202
01:01:42,355 --> 01:01:44,725
for this moment.

1203
01:01:45,195 --> 01:01:46,195
"That's right."

1204
01:01:47,195 --> 01:01:49,994
"Hardships have always been necessary..."

1205
01:01:49,995 --> 01:01:53,235
"for a happy ending."

1206
01:01:53,565 --> 01:01:56,175
I had that thought.

1207
01:01:56,775 --> 01:01:58,004
Really?

1208
01:01:58,005 --> 01:01:59,844
(Si Woo and Hee Dong finally get their 1-on-1 date.)

1209
01:01:59,845 --> 01:02:01,414
She went through a lot.

1210
01:02:01,415 --> 01:02:03,114
- I know.
- Nam Jung...

1211
01:02:03,115 --> 01:02:04,745
also has a smile...

1212
01:02:04,985 --> 01:02:06,215
on his face.

1213
01:02:06,615 --> 01:02:07,615
Eun Byul.

1214
01:02:08,185 --> 01:02:09,955
There is something big outside.

1215
01:02:10,155 --> 01:02:11,185
What?

1216
01:02:11,885 --> 01:02:13,325
Go outside and look.

1217
01:02:14,895 --> 01:02:16,055
Outside the door.

1218
01:02:16,695 --> 01:02:17,695
What?

1219
01:02:17,865 --> 01:02:19,425
If you go outside the door,

1220
01:02:21,035 --> 01:02:22,535
you'll see something big.

1221
01:02:24,665 --> 01:02:25,704
The door.

1222
01:02:25,705 --> 01:02:27,004
(Eun Byul goes to check the board.)

1223
01:02:27,005 --> 01:02:28,404
- Eun Byul is going.
- Oh, no.

1224
01:02:28,405 --> 01:02:29,805
Eun Byul is going.

1225
01:02:30,235 --> 01:02:32,904
Eun Byul might become upset upon seeing the board.

1226
01:02:32,905 --> 01:02:34,315
She might feel victimized.

1227
01:02:37,545 --> 01:02:38,715
Eun Byul.

1228
01:02:40,955 --> 01:02:42,085
Eun Byul, look.

1229
01:02:43,855 --> 01:02:45,685
Good morning.

1230
01:02:45,785 --> 01:02:47,525
Why are you saying it so politely?

1231
01:02:48,955 --> 01:02:52,925
(Shin Jae Hyuk, Woo Seo Yoon)

1232
01:02:53,465 --> 01:02:56,165
Everyone was matched up.

1233
01:02:56,395 --> 01:02:59,564
Jae Hyuk was matched up with Seo Yoon.

1234
01:02:59,565 --> 01:03:00,875
(Shin Jae Hyuk, Woo Seo Yoon)

1235
01:03:01,105 --> 01:03:05,505
I'll be lying if I say that I don't mind.

1236
01:03:06,045 --> 01:03:08,075
My head was about to explode.

1237
01:03:08,345 --> 01:03:11,015
I felt a bit confused.

1238
01:03:11,345 --> 01:03:14,955
I still don't know what Jae Hyuk is thinking.

1239
01:03:15,115 --> 01:03:17,624
Eun Byul was the last one to see the board.

1240
01:03:17,625 --> 01:03:19,724
Jae Hyuk had no choice...

1241
01:03:19,725 --> 01:03:21,794
but to put his name on the empty section.

1242
01:03:21,795 --> 01:03:25,924
But Eun Byul doesn't know who wrote the name first...

1243
01:03:25,925 --> 01:03:27,234
- between Seo Yoon and Jae Hyuk.
- She doesn't know.

1244
01:03:27,235 --> 01:03:29,834
- She doesn't know.
- So she might misunderstand...

1245
01:03:29,835 --> 01:03:30,934
this situation.

1246
01:03:30,935 --> 01:03:35,604
The 2 of them spent time together until 4:30am last night.

1247
01:03:35,605 --> 01:03:39,175
But she came out to see Jae Hyuk matched up with another woman.

1248
01:03:39,805 --> 01:03:42,845
She'd naturally think, "What is he playing at?"

1249
01:03:43,375 --> 01:03:44,844
She'd misunderstand.

1250
01:03:44,845 --> 01:03:47,184
- It's natural to misunderstand.
- Of course.

1251
01:03:47,185 --> 01:03:48,755
I'd misunderstand and get upset.

1252
01:03:48,915 --> 01:03:50,784
May I go and talk to Jae Hyuk?

1253
01:03:50,785 --> 01:03:51,785
- Seriously.
- It's too late.

1254
01:03:51,786 --> 01:03:54,425
- I want to ask what he is thinking.
- I really want to ask.

1255
01:03:57,765 --> 01:03:58,894
(Jae Hyuk leaves quietly.)

1256
01:03:58,895 --> 01:04:00,224
Your outfit suits you.

1257
01:04:00,225 --> 01:04:01,865
(Jae Hyuk leaves quietly.)

1258
01:04:03,035 --> 01:04:04,705
Am I supposed to write my name on it?

1259
01:04:06,665 --> 01:04:08,204
That's right. He is stepping away.

1260
01:04:08,205 --> 01:04:09,304
He is stepping away because he feels bad.

1261
01:04:09,305 --> 01:04:11,245
- He should've said something.
- I know.

1262
01:04:11,875 --> 01:04:13,775
(Sighing)

1263
01:04:17,185 --> 01:04:19,315
I worried about what Eun Byul would think.

1264
01:04:20,185 --> 01:04:22,315
When Eun Byul saw it,

1265
01:04:22,885 --> 01:04:24,855
I had already been matched up...

1266
01:04:25,125 --> 01:04:28,125
with Seo Yoon.

1267
01:04:29,655 --> 01:04:31,925
I thought it might be confusing for her.

1268
01:04:42,005 --> 01:04:43,474
Shall I change all of them?

1269
01:04:43,475 --> 01:04:44,874
Push the names down by one.

1270
01:04:44,875 --> 01:04:47,075
- What? Shall I do that?
- You could push them up by one.

1271
01:04:47,445 --> 01:04:48,675
Hold on.

1272
01:04:49,875 --> 01:04:52,485
(Eun Byul goes back inside without writing her name.)

1273
01:04:52,885 --> 01:04:55,684
Eun Byul didn't write her name next to Jae Seung's.

1274
01:04:55,685 --> 01:04:57,385
- She left without writing her name.
- She looked at the board.

1275
01:04:57,685 --> 01:05:00,454
Writing the name is required, right?

1276
01:05:00,455 --> 01:05:01,994
- Exactly.
- It's required,

1277
01:05:01,995 --> 01:05:04,265
but Eun Byul was too confused to write her name.

1278
01:05:04,325 --> 01:05:05,624
She was too flustered...

1279
01:05:05,625 --> 01:05:07,765
- to write her name.
- She didn't write it.

1280
01:05:10,765 --> 01:05:11,765
Did you see it?

1281
01:05:14,175 --> 01:05:15,305
What's going on?

1282
01:05:15,475 --> 01:05:16,575
I'm taken aback.

1283
01:05:17,135 --> 01:05:18,875
- Did you write your name?
- No, I didn't.

1284
01:05:19,075 --> 01:05:20,075
Didn't you write your name?

1285
01:05:21,775 --> 01:05:22,845
Why not?

1286
01:05:24,215 --> 01:05:26,385
I was just taken aback.

1287
01:05:29,115 --> 01:05:30,155
Interesting.

1288
01:05:31,725 --> 01:05:32,855
This isn't easy.

1289
01:05:34,895 --> 01:05:36,525
Gosh, what's this?

1290
01:05:38,665 --> 01:05:39,695
Yesterday,

1291
01:05:40,765 --> 01:05:42,094
you guys were together until late at night, right?

1292
01:05:42,095 --> 01:05:43,395
Yes, until late at night.

1293
01:05:45,605 --> 01:05:47,574
When Eun Byul is extremely angry,

1294
01:05:47,575 --> 01:05:49,075
she says, "Interesting."

1295
01:05:49,335 --> 01:05:50,475
"Interesting."

1296
01:05:57,415 --> 01:05:59,444
(Eun Byul writes her name next to Jae Seung's.)

1297
01:05:59,445 --> 01:06:01,014
She writes her name.

1298
01:06:01,015 --> 01:06:03,314
- She writes her name.
- She has to do it.

1299
01:06:03,315 --> 01:06:05,584
(Jae Seung, Cho Eun Byul)

1300
01:06:05,585 --> 01:06:10,325
(Everyone has been matched up for a date.)

1301
01:06:10,525 --> 01:06:12,225
It'd totally get on her nerves.

1302
01:06:12,925 --> 01:06:14,264
It'd annoy her so much.

1303
01:06:14,265 --> 01:06:16,635
It could be hard on Eun Byul.

1304
01:06:16,995 --> 01:06:19,664
You know, the smallest thing...

1305
01:06:19,665 --> 01:06:22,075
- like what we've seen...
- I know.

1306
01:06:22,435 --> 01:06:24,544
- could mess up the relationship.
- Of course. Love is like that.

1307
01:06:24,545 --> 01:06:27,715
That's right. Conflicts begin from the smallest thing.

1308
01:06:27,915 --> 01:06:30,574
Jae Hyuk's heart could lean toward Eun Byul...

1309
01:06:30,575 --> 01:06:33,284
with the ratio of 6 to 4 or 7 to 3,

1310
01:06:33,285 --> 01:06:35,184
but he got matched up to a different person...

1311
01:06:35,185 --> 01:06:37,255
- on the board for a date.
- Right.

1312
01:06:37,425 --> 01:06:40,124
- It could be a big variable.
- I agree.

1313
01:06:40,125 --> 01:06:42,795
This date is very important.

1314
01:06:43,455 --> 01:06:46,194
At what time did you go to bed?

1315
01:06:46,195 --> 01:06:48,495
- It's Jae Seung. Finally.
- This could be interesting.

1316
01:06:49,065 --> 01:06:53,505
All of us talked loudly in the kitchen until 2:30am.

1317
01:06:53,705 --> 01:06:54,433
I see.

1318
01:06:55,635 --> 01:06:57,175
The old members were gone, after all.

1319
01:06:59,545 --> 01:07:00,674
It wasn't like that.

1320
01:07:00,675 --> 01:07:03,114
We decided to have a pajama party today.

1321
01:07:03,115 --> 01:07:04,145
I see.

1322
01:07:04,745 --> 01:07:06,315
The two of them are wearing matching looks.

1323
01:07:06,885 --> 01:07:08,084
- You're right.
- Yes.

1324
01:07:08,085 --> 01:07:09,385
It looks like things are going well.

1325
01:07:09,785 --> 01:07:11,754
When you first moved here, how was your Korean?

1326
01:07:11,755 --> 01:07:14,025
I had to... I had to learn.

1327
01:07:14,625 --> 01:07:16,155
I took private lessons.

1328
01:07:16,355 --> 01:07:17,765
- For Korean?
- Yes.

1329
01:07:18,565 --> 01:07:21,864
But when my private tutor came,

1330
01:07:21,865 --> 01:07:23,565
I hid in the house.

1331
01:07:24,205 --> 01:07:26,205
- I didn't want to take the lessons.
- Korean is more difficult...

1332
01:07:26,305 --> 01:07:27,674
- right.
- than English.

1333
01:07:27,675 --> 01:07:28,675
I know.

1334
01:07:29,405 --> 01:07:31,004
So until high school...

1335
01:07:31,005 --> 01:07:32,874
Jae Hyuk, say something.

1336
01:07:32,875 --> 01:07:34,114
Tell her that it wasn't your intention.

1337
01:07:34,115 --> 01:07:36,215
- I think he is there to say that.
- It must've been hard.

1338
01:07:37,545 --> 01:07:39,085
(Glancing over)

1339
01:07:39,945 --> 01:07:40,955
Did you get some sleep?

1340
01:07:41,315 --> 01:07:42,914
I woke up at 11am.

1341
01:07:42,915 --> 01:07:44,225
- Really?
- Yes.

1342
01:07:44,455 --> 01:07:45,725
You slept more than I did.

1343
01:07:58,005 --> 01:08:02,475
(There is awkwardness in the air.)

1344
01:08:11,385 --> 01:08:13,985
Talk things out before leaving for a date.

1345
01:08:14,685 --> 01:08:16,954
I thought Jae Hyuk would explain himself,

1346
01:08:16,955 --> 01:08:18,484
- but he isn't doing that actively.
- I know.

1347
01:08:18,485 --> 01:08:20,554
Since he was with her until late at night,

1348
01:08:20,555 --> 01:08:21,725
he should clear her misunderstanding.

1349
01:08:22,625 --> 01:08:25,895
(Seo Yoon appears after making preparations.)

1350
01:08:26,765 --> 01:08:29,435
(Glancing over)

1351
01:08:41,645 --> 01:08:42,645
Shall we go?

1352
01:08:48,685 --> 01:08:50,055
See you later, everyone.

1353
01:08:50,115 --> 01:08:51,124
Have fun.

1354
01:08:51,125 --> 01:08:52,355
Have a nice date.

1355
01:08:53,785 --> 01:08:54,955
See you later, everyone.

1356
01:08:55,155 --> 01:08:56,224
Have fun.

1357
01:08:56,225 --> 01:08:57,325
Have a nice date.

1358
01:08:57,625 --> 01:08:58,665
See you later.

1359
01:09:01,365 --> 01:09:05,905
(Jae Hyuk and Eun Byul couldn't say anything.)

1360
01:09:10,535 --> 01:09:14,645
(The last date before the Final Selection)

1361
01:09:15,345 --> 01:09:17,444
(What changes...)

1362
01:09:17,445 --> 01:09:20,285
(will today's date bring?)

1363
01:09:25,985 --> 01:09:30,655
(The last 1-on-1 Date, You Hee Dong and Park Si Woo)

1364
01:09:30,995 --> 01:09:33,224
- My goodness.
- Look at them.

1365
01:09:33,225 --> 01:09:34,294
Here we go.

1366
01:09:34,295 --> 01:09:36,964
They're having their first date...

1367
01:09:36,965 --> 01:09:39,104
the day before the Final Selection.

1368
01:09:39,105 --> 01:09:40,165
- That's right.
- Yes.

1369
01:09:41,835 --> 01:09:44,205
- It snowed a lot yesterday.
- I know.

1370
01:09:44,675 --> 01:09:47,615
When I woke up, everything was white.

1371
01:09:48,115 --> 01:09:49,475
It was very pretty.

1372
01:09:50,315 --> 01:09:51,985
It snowed a lot at night.

1373
01:09:52,585 --> 01:09:56,585
(They begin the conversation with what happened last night.)

1374
01:09:57,455 --> 01:09:58,855
Apparently, it was really nice.

1375
01:09:59,355 --> 01:10:02,795
- I guess they went to a hotel.
- A resort.

1376
01:10:04,465 --> 01:10:05,825
Maybe I should've sent it yesterday.

1377
01:10:07,195 --> 01:10:08,195
Yes.

1378
01:10:09,065 --> 01:10:10,195
We should've sent it yesterday.

1379
01:10:10,635 --> 01:10:12,305
- What?
- We should've sent it yesterday.

1380
01:10:14,175 --> 01:10:16,535
- The two of us could've had fun.
- You should've sent it!

1381
01:10:16,675 --> 01:10:19,805
You should've sent it! What were you thinking?

1382
01:10:20,945 --> 01:10:23,445
You know, it was like... Hear me out.

1383
01:10:23,575 --> 01:10:25,644
Had I known...

1384
01:10:25,645 --> 01:10:28,785
about your feelings,

1385
01:10:28,815 --> 01:10:30,115
I would've definitely sent the message.

1386
01:10:31,725 --> 01:10:32,855
I would've definitely sent it.

1387
01:10:34,425 --> 01:10:36,155
But I didn't know because you kept quiet.

1388
01:10:36,355 --> 01:10:37,355
You fool.

1389
01:10:39,195 --> 01:10:44,605
(Si Woo complains with affection.)

1390
01:10:45,965 --> 01:10:49,405
When you saw me on the first day,

1391
01:10:49,575 --> 01:10:51,245
how did you feel?

1392
01:10:52,945 --> 01:10:54,105
Be completely honest.

1393
01:10:54,415 --> 01:10:55,415
Upon arrival?

1394
01:10:57,115 --> 01:10:58,115
- Hello.
- Hello.

1395
01:10:58,116 --> 01:11:01,715
(Hee Dong came like a present on the first day.)

1396
01:11:02,185 --> 01:11:05,085
(Si Woo was shy.)

1397
01:11:05,925 --> 01:11:12,065
(Hee Dong handed her flowers for the First Impression Selection.)

1398
01:11:13,295 --> 01:11:15,395
When you saw me on the first day,

1399
01:11:15,635 --> 01:11:17,135
how did you feel?

1400
01:11:21,175 --> 01:11:22,405
Upon arrival?

1401
01:11:23,935 --> 01:11:25,145
I thought you were pretty.

1402
01:11:27,375 --> 01:11:28,415
Thanks.

1403
01:11:32,015 --> 01:11:35,054
(Hee Dong expresses himself without hesitation.)

1404
01:11:35,055 --> 01:11:37,055
- Look at him.
- Right now,

1405
01:11:37,155 --> 01:11:39,855
things will go crazy with the smallest spark.

1406
01:11:40,955 --> 01:11:44,825
(They can't hide their smiles.)

1407
01:11:45,625 --> 01:11:46,695
What do you think about being here?

1408
01:11:47,225 --> 01:11:49,834
- Firstly, it's a new experience.
- Yes.

1409
01:11:49,835 --> 01:11:52,205
- Meeting like this is fate.
- You're right.

1410
01:11:52,765 --> 01:11:54,575
It's fate. It's total fate.

1411
01:11:56,005 --> 01:11:57,945
I'll talk about you a lot when I go home.

1412
01:12:02,168 --> 01:12:03,268
That you liked me a lot?

1413
01:12:08,185 --> 01:12:09,285
It's understandable.

1414
01:12:11,055 --> 01:12:12,754
- Hee Dong...
- "That you liked me a lot?"

1415
01:12:12,755 --> 01:12:13,755
"That you liked me a lot?"

1416
01:12:13,756 --> 01:12:14,995
He glanced over at her.

1417
01:12:15,225 --> 01:12:17,094
I want to tease them.

1418
01:12:17,095 --> 01:12:19,395
(Si Woo smiles shyly as if he had read her mind.)

1419
01:12:21,365 --> 01:12:23,665
Go to your dad and tell him...

1420
01:12:24,195 --> 01:12:26,305
that you found your dream girl...

1421
01:12:27,365 --> 01:12:28,605
at the age of 20.

1422
01:12:34,205 --> 01:12:36,144
What's going on? What?

1423
01:12:36,145 --> 01:12:38,744
(Si Woo's straightforward comment is unexpected.)

1424
01:12:38,745 --> 01:12:39,885
Si Woo!

1425
01:12:41,455 --> 01:12:43,155
She likes him so much.

1426
01:12:44,385 --> 01:12:47,325
Did Hee Dong tell you that he found his dream girl?

1427
01:12:48,625 --> 01:12:49,625
Tae Woong.

1428
01:12:49,995 --> 01:12:51,095
Did she do that at home?

1429
01:12:51,365 --> 01:12:54,194
- She rarely talks to me.
- Really?

1430
01:12:54,195 --> 01:12:55,764
- I see.
- Even when I ask...

1431
01:12:55,765 --> 01:12:58,234
They aren't allowed to give any spoilers to the parents.

1432
01:12:58,235 --> 01:12:59,364
- Exactly.
- That's right.

1433
01:12:59,365 --> 01:13:01,735
My daughter asked me what manual therapy was.

1434
01:13:02,735 --> 01:13:05,205
It's a secret. She shouldn't have asked.

1435
01:13:07,715 --> 01:13:10,014
(The atmosphere is sweet.)

1436
01:13:10,015 --> 01:13:12,885
(What's the location of the first date?)

1437
01:13:15,515 --> 01:13:17,155
Are we seriously doing this?

1438
01:13:24,595 --> 01:13:27,424
We first went to an indoor batting cage.

1439
01:13:27,425 --> 01:13:28,635
(Indoor batting cage)

1440
01:13:29,065 --> 01:13:30,765
Indoor batting cage.

1441
01:13:30,865 --> 01:13:32,104
He was determined to look cool.

1442
01:13:32,105 --> 01:13:33,465
(The perfect date for Hee Dong to show his charms)

1443
01:13:34,705 --> 01:13:36,834
- Have you done it before?
- Never.

1444
01:13:36,835 --> 01:13:38,105
Isn't it hard?

1445
01:13:39,045 --> 01:13:41,215
I don't think I'll be able to hit the ball.

1446
01:13:46,515 --> 01:13:48,085
Let me warm up first.

1447
01:13:50,885 --> 01:13:55,395
(Hee Dong warms up by swinging the bat.)

1448
01:14:01,235 --> 01:14:03,535
I'll imagine this is a game and play.

1449
01:14:04,405 --> 01:14:05,805
No pressure.

1450
01:14:06,965 --> 01:14:09,235
(Hee Dong changes his position.)

1451
01:14:11,875 --> 01:14:14,205
(He easily hits the ball.)

1452
01:14:14,645 --> 01:14:16,344
(He sure is a baseball player.)

1453
01:14:16,345 --> 01:14:17,515
Oh, he did it easily.

1454
01:14:19,415 --> 01:14:20,515
You're good.

1455
01:14:20,915 --> 01:14:23,015
- Are you getting the hang of it?
- I am.

1456
01:14:24,625 --> 01:14:25,755
No.

1457
01:14:26,925 --> 01:14:30,025
(One more perfect swing)

1458
01:14:32,395 --> 01:14:33,395
Cool.

1459
01:14:33,396 --> 01:14:34,965
- That's really cool.
- He really showed her.

1460
01:14:38,765 --> 01:14:39,649
Good.

1461
01:14:41,805 --> 01:14:42,904
- Nice.
- What's she going to do?

1462
01:14:42,905 --> 01:14:44,745
That ends it.

1463
01:14:44,875 --> 01:14:47,405
- She'll fall for him again.
- He looks perfect.

1464
01:14:47,436 --> 01:14:49,236
- He's a baseball player.
- Of course.

1465
01:14:49,715 --> 01:14:51,485
Do you want to try?

1466
01:14:51,585 --> 01:14:53,085
(Nodding)

1467
01:14:54,485 --> 01:14:55,485
But...

1468
01:14:56,455 --> 01:14:58,425
- Can you help me?
- But...

1469
01:14:59,155 --> 01:15:00,685
Stand here.

1470
01:15:00,885 --> 01:15:02,054
(Si Woo enters the ground for the first time.)

1471
01:15:02,055 --> 01:15:04,155
If I stand here, it starts right away, doesn't it?

1472
01:15:04,895 --> 01:15:06,795
Choke up on the bat.

1473
01:15:07,095 --> 01:15:08,835
- They're about to hold hands.
- Choke up on the bat.

1474
01:15:09,695 --> 01:15:11,064
- That went smooth.
- Like that.

1475
01:15:11,065 --> 01:15:13,005
- That's smooth.
- Try to see the ball.

1476
01:15:14,735 --> 01:15:16,135
Hit when he holds it.

1477
01:15:16,235 --> 01:15:17,805
Don't hit yet. Only for the timing.

1478
01:15:17,945 --> 01:15:19,574
- Okay. For the timing.
- Only for the timing.

1479
01:15:19,575 --> 01:15:21,715
So you'd know when to swing.

1480
01:15:22,745 --> 01:15:24,615
Move your hands like this.

1481
01:15:25,545 --> 01:15:27,915
- What?
- Swing from behind.

1482
01:15:29,515 --> 01:15:32,055
When you hold the bat...

1483
01:15:32,385 --> 01:15:34,355
(Hesitant)

1484
01:15:34,755 --> 01:15:36,254
(Look at that boy.)

1485
01:15:36,255 --> 01:15:37,724
- But it was unavoidable.
- The bad hand.

1486
01:15:37,725 --> 01:15:40,194
- That's necessary.
- He could've...

1487
01:15:40,195 --> 01:15:41,434
just explained it to her.

1488
01:15:41,435 --> 01:15:42,735
(He could've explained it to her.)

1489
01:15:42,895 --> 01:15:45,134
When you hold the bat,

1490
01:15:45,135 --> 01:15:46,835
you need to stretch your legs a bit.

1491
01:15:47,565 --> 01:15:49,405
Yes. Move your left leg forward.

1492
01:15:49,505 --> 01:15:50,634
- Try to see the ball.
- Can I see it again?

1493
01:15:50,635 --> 01:15:51,775
Okay.

1494
01:15:52,175 --> 01:15:56,245
It felt like Hee Dong didn't know what to do.

1495
01:15:57,115 --> 01:15:59,844
I could feel that he was hesitant...

1496
01:15:59,845 --> 01:16:02,555
behind me.

1497
01:16:03,015 --> 01:16:07,125
"He wants to teach me,"

1498
01:16:07,755 --> 01:16:10,195
"but is he too nervous?"

1499
01:16:10,495 --> 01:16:12,065
That's what I thought.

1500
01:16:13,125 --> 01:16:14,195
I thought that was cute.

1501
01:16:16,035 --> 01:16:17,231
Why don't you try by yourself?

1502
01:16:17,891 --> 01:16:20,005
- Try it?
- Keep your hands together.

1503
01:16:21,235 --> 01:16:22,604
(First try)

1504
01:16:22,605 --> 01:16:24,745
(Failed)

1505
01:16:25,845 --> 01:16:27,244
Am I not strong enough?

1506
01:16:27,245 --> 01:16:28,775
Do I need to swing more forward?

1507
01:16:29,075 --> 01:16:30,815
Can you teach me one more time?

1508
01:16:32,215 --> 01:16:34,955
Keep your hands together. That makes it easier to swing.

1509
01:16:35,234 --> 01:16:36,284
Look.

1510
01:16:36,285 --> 01:16:38,785
If you hold it like this,

1511
01:16:39,325 --> 01:16:41,295
it's easier to swing.

1512
01:16:41,455 --> 01:16:42,525
- Like this?
- Yes.

1513
01:16:42,825 --> 01:16:45,065
As if you were hitting from here.

1514
01:16:46,125 --> 01:16:47,324
From here...

1515
01:16:47,325 --> 01:16:48,494
(Getting even closer)

1516
01:16:48,495 --> 01:16:49,935
You have to go up.

1517
01:16:50,665 --> 01:16:51,965
- Go up.
- Like this?

1518
01:16:52,735 --> 01:16:53,835
- Okay.
- Give it a try.

1519
01:16:54,775 --> 01:16:56,375
- There you go.
- There you go.

1520
01:16:56,775 --> 01:16:58,145
It's over.

1521
01:16:58,305 --> 01:17:00,845
- Can Si Woo even focus?
- He held her from the back.

1522
01:17:02,115 --> 01:17:03,314
Yes. Nice swing.

1523
01:17:03,315 --> 01:17:04,415
- Is this right?
- Yes.

1524
01:17:06,745 --> 01:17:08,515
(Exclaiming)

1525
01:17:09,655 --> 01:17:11,625
(Her second try is successful thanks to Hee Dong's help.)

1526
01:17:14,555 --> 01:17:15,595
Good.

1527
01:17:17,725 --> 01:17:18,965
She kind of looked cute.

1528
01:17:20,465 --> 01:17:25,835
Si Woo was pretty enthusiastic.

1529
01:17:26,105 --> 01:17:27,465
That's what I liked about her.

1530
01:17:28,802 --> 01:17:30,002
Are your hands okay?

1531
01:17:31,405 --> 01:17:33,505
- What?
- You're sweating so much.

1532
01:17:35,415 --> 01:17:39,015
(Si Woo's unexpected touch)

1533
01:17:39,485 --> 01:17:40,785
- Did you have fun?
- Yes.

1534
01:17:43,355 --> 01:17:45,225
Today was a new experience.

1535
01:17:45,925 --> 01:17:47,954
You really dressed up today.

1536
01:17:47,955 --> 01:17:49,225
No, it's fine.

1537
01:17:50,025 --> 01:17:51,395
- Do you want to go eat?
- Yes.

1538
01:17:51,565 --> 01:17:53,025
- Let's go.
- Let's go eat.

1539
01:17:55,795 --> 01:17:57,465
Yes. Do whatever you want now.

1540
01:17:58,005 --> 01:17:59,204
- That's sweet.
- Now...

1541
01:17:59,205 --> 01:18:00,904
Now they're like...

1542
01:18:00,905 --> 01:18:02,574
(Their unforgettable sweet moment)

1543
01:18:02,575 --> 01:18:04,304
"Good job. You're sweating."

1544
01:18:04,305 --> 01:18:05,305
I know.

1545
01:18:05,605 --> 01:18:08,675
- Gosh.
- They'll be smiling a lot.

1546
01:18:09,015 --> 01:18:10,314
That's how they seem.

1547
01:18:10,315 --> 01:18:12,844
- They get along.
- They like each other now.

1548
01:18:12,845 --> 01:18:14,115
You're in-laws now.

1549
01:18:16,315 --> 01:18:19,625
(Who will continue this excitement?)

1550
01:18:20,625 --> 01:18:23,555
(Shin Jae Hyuk and Woo Seo Yoon's last 1-on-1 Date)

1551
01:18:23,995 --> 01:18:25,595
- They are...
- These two.

1552
01:18:25,765 --> 01:18:27,624
- They are...
- This is the highlight.

1553
01:18:27,625 --> 01:18:29,194
Sit tight, everyone.

1554
01:18:29,195 --> 01:18:31,134
- Will there be a twist or not?
- Right.

1555
01:18:31,135 --> 01:18:32,434
- Here it comes.
